text: Bernadett Balázs (born 19 April 1975) is a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
